duck: Marie-Pierre Leray - Marie-Pierre Leray (born 17 February 1975 in Villecresens) is a French figure skater.
Francis Xavier Leray - Francis Xavier Leray was a French-born prelate of the Roman Catholic Church.
David Leray - David Leray is a French football defender.
In 1947 he became a professor at the College de France.
